ote>幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有幾個位個音唔啱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大霧 同 鎖匙</blockquote><br />\n大霧好似無問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外巴打係咪想講「鑰匙」？</blockquote><br />\n係押韻<br />\n不過覺得有點怪</blockquote><br />\n反而覺得以下幾隻字有啲唔啱音：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">沒</span>風聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">找</span>不<span style=\"color: red;\">到</span> (雖然原詞都係寫 分不<span style=\"color: red;\">到</span>)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">避</span>風港"},{"pid":"bcd4f011c9d6c8e61270fcbdaa50d4b4e8243250","tid":256403,"uid":61750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有幾個位個音唔啱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大霧 同 鎖匙</blockquote><br />\n大霧好似無問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外巴打係咪想講「鑰匙」？</blockquote><br />\n係押韻<br />\n不過覺得有點怪</blockquote><br />\n反而覺得以下幾隻字有啲唔啱音：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">沒</span>風聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">找</span>不<span style=\"color: red;\">到</span> (雖然原詞都係寫 分不<span style=\"color: red;\">到</span>)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">避</span>風港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒字同原詞好似同音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面個兩個我填嗰陣唔係好覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我再睇睇 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea64564cd62c36849b6197fed3146ff0a107a79","tid":256403,"uid":61750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持創作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b